com.misc.common.moplaf.dbsynch

Interface DbSynchUnit

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DbSynchUnitAbstract, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DbSynchUnitImpl

    public interface DbSynchUnit
extends DbSynchUnitAbstract
    A representation of the model object 'DbSynchUnit'.

    A DbSynchUnit is a non-root unit in the hiearchy of the synch units. Typically it represents a group of tables that must be queried together, with the same parameter values.

    The following features are supported:

    • Parent Unit
    See Also:
